other_research_comments: Verified from Stanislaus County EMS Agency ambulance rates webpage - IFT Non-Emergency
research_notes: Source is Stanislaus County EMS Agency rates webpage (HTML table). County sets 911 emergency rates for exclusive operating area providers; IFT providers file their own rates (county does not set/limit IFT rates). 911 zones: Zone 4 & D (Del Puerto), Zone 5 (AMR), Zone A (Oak Valley), Zone W (Westside). HCPCS mapping: 911 uses A0427 (ALS-E), A0429 (BLS-E), A0433 (ALS2), A0998 (non-transport), A0425 (mileage); IFT uses A0426 (ALS-NE), A0428 (BLS-NE), A0434 (SCT/CCT), A0425 (mileage).
